</ul>
</li>
<li>74,000–120,000 <a href="/wiki/Fungi" title="Fungi" class="mw-redirect">fungi</a>;<sup id="cite_ref-Hawksworth_36-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Hawksworth-36" title=""><span>[</span>37<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
