<li id="cite_note-bulletin28-55">^ <a href="#cite_ref-bulletin28_55-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-bulletin28_55-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="http://www.farmedia.org/bulletins/bulletin28.html" class="external text" title="http://www.farmedia.org/bulletins/bulletin28.html" rel="nofollow">“Genetic Pollution: The Great Genetic Scandal”; Devinder Sharma can be contacted at: 7 Triveni Apartments, A-6 Paschim Vihar, New Delhi-110 063, India. Email: dsharma@ndf.vsnl.net.in. Centre for alternative agricultural media (CAAM).</a> <a href="http://www.infochangeindia.org/features43.jsp" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.infochangeindia.org/features43.jsp" rel="nofollow">[5]</a></li>
