<li><a href="http://dmoz.org/Science/Environment/Biodiversity/" class="external text" title="http://dmoz.org/Science/Environment/Biodiversity/" rel="nofollow">DMOZ</a> - Open Directory Project.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.eol.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.eol.org/" rel="nofollow">Encyclopedia of Life</a> - Documenting all species of life on earth.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.searchnbn.net" class="external text" title="http://www.searchnbn.net" rel="nofollow">National Biodiversity Network</a> - NBN Gateway.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.stanford.edu/group/microdocs/" class="external text" title="http://www.stanford.edu/group/microdocs/" rel="nofollow">Microdocs</a>, <a href="http://www.stanford.edu/group/microdocs/diversity.html" class="external text" title="http://www.stanford.edu/group/microdocs/diversity.html" rel="nofollow">Diversity.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.economics.noaa.gov/?goal=ecosystems&amp;file=users/business/species/" class="external text" title="http://www.economics.noaa.gov/?goal=ecosystems&amp;file=users/business/species/" rel="nofollow">Economics of Species protection &amp; Management</a> NOAA Economics</li>
</ul>


